<ul><li><i><a href="/wiki/4_Little_Girls" title="4 Little Girls">4 Little Girls</a></i> (1997)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Big_One_(film)" title="The Big One (film)">The Big One</a></i> (1998)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Buena_Vista_Social_Club_(film)" title="Buena Vista Social Club (film)">Buena Vista Social Club</a></i> (1999)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/The_Filth_and_the_Fury" title="The Filth and the Fury">The Filth and the Fury</a></i> (2000)</li>
<li><i><a href="/wiki/Startup.com" title="Startup.com">Startup.com</a></i> (2001)</li>
